item.description:
As well as having to Skype enable all users recently (see previous post) I also had to mailbox enable the users. With Exchange 2010 you can&rsquo;t just import the powershell module. Using this article as a base I came up with this;
$Session = New-Pssession -COnfigurationName Microsoft.Exchange -ConnectionUri http://exchangeservername/powershell
Import-Pssession $Session
Get-User -OrganizationalUnit &ldquo;OU=ExampleOU,DC=Example,DC=Com&rdquo; | Enable-Mailbox -database &ldquo;your mailbox database&rdquo;
